headline.main: Rain-Hit Brasil Open Final to Be Completed on Monday
headline.print_headline: Rain-Hit Brasil Open Final to Be Completed on Monday

lead_paragraph: The final of the Brasil Open was interrupted by rain on Sunday and will recommence on Monday with Spaniard Albert Ramos-Vinolas leading Pablo Cuevas 7-6(3) 3-3.
